      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability and opportunity, whether for basic daily use, a backup vehicle, or a project. An honest-value option with plenty of potential for the right owner.",
