    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts conversations and still has a lot to offer as a budget commuter, starter car, or weekend project. A great chance to get into something inexpensive without spending a fortune, and it\u2019s being offered by someone who believes in being straightforward and easy to deal with. If you want simple, honest value and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a really solid find.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest project car with great bones and plenty of upside for the right buyer. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of analog driving character enthusiasts appreciate. Not a showpiece, but a usable platform for a budget build, parts donor, or weekend wrenching project. If you know your way around maintenance and want something with real potential, this is a compelling entry point.",
      "price": 6900.0,
