      "description": "This car has the kind of lived-in character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a seasoned machine with stories in its panels and plenty of road left for the right driver. It\u2019s an ideal find for someone who sees potential, whether you want an inexpensive runabout, a hands-on project, or a practical set of wheels with personality. Honest, unpretentious, and priced to move, it offers a chance to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
